{"id":"8be3aa05f33c01c5d24d38bc35df6caf0ef01c0e12765e6a636065189908155d","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:0","text":"此节点允许艺术家使用 3D 投影放置图案，而不是使用通常用于依赖 UVs 的纹理的 2D 方案。它允许选择 Pref（用于变形网格），并指定要变换到的坐标系统。"}
{"id":"e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:1","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"id":"f102986b39effb31080ae442f61febe7ed58df1515c0711ccfadfe0311ccec81","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:2","text":"Scale"}
{"id":"57caaae863c454be1208dad3283238ba9eb966648077ecddc0090b3f640badcc","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:3","text":"在 3D 中对特征频率进行统一 Scale（缩放）。"}
{"id":"c36d819e7bc6d2b7da51394411c733db89c395987885ca6770167a3b9bc45c3c","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:4","text":"Use"}
{"id":"b43b4b5eed3bd419d70312125e292b4f75a847bd1d048887e09dd0011d97b40a","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:5","text":"选择你想使用的 position 类型。"}
{"id":"8d59829c1e15afe1a7fae93e8e5e32d8511bec5fd598a09f4fea6033b31e8a66","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:6","text":"Usage"}
{"id":"8e37953d23daca5ff01b8282c33f4e0a2152f1d1885f94c06418617e3ee1d24e","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:7","text":"Value"}
{"id":"4e75423cb7643b0da7ab3da2d16e0831bd5d1130812387b83c4ddcb2f352c7fc","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:8","text":"Default variable"}
{"id":"18ec820bf8dcf2b0a01b55638bff1977ea7a240cf7e8d9ff4c57251216852155","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:9","text":"Current position: P"}
{"id":"5754addaf5911578d9bf115263359b13de0e537eff0dd14ec6548709490ae311","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:10","text":"使用当前（已置换的）surface position"}
{"id":"d36549bd5b82f1f5520772454a5d3651c2369818b56ea511e3f3ca71a71efc08","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:11","text":"Undisplaced position: Po"}
{"id":"ff978c35a702d7c0ba1670dd50d42f80f1efbf9d17f6e4c240bd4a648273a0d5","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:12","text":"使用"}
{"id":"6db7d803e74f1ffa7d8f5adc0bf95b3e15bf4c8373fffadf546227cc6c6742cb","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:13","text":"置换前"}
{"id":"4d94d77305562a29d5299fd3c28a21f7d2cb0f0f8681d71a64d2ddb2f5d2dbac","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:14","text":"的 surface position"}
{"id":"1419b38716afb25ce89d64bd88006fc0cfcdf1dac05e188ee4be7498ffcff4ca","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:15","text":"Deform : __Pref"}
{"id":"65b0fdf57e277549a863b9ab0090bda13b4d2f4cfcaf34c4c5f5a3d473cbcbe7","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:16","text":"使用 object space 中的 reference position primitive variable（参考位置 primitive variable）"}
{"id":"2f4a5b034c898054c0156b207fd5e134a5a9513e37c7016818be983b2506a65e","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:17","text":"Deform & transform: __WPref"}
{"id":"25fe93c46e161809f4dd9600a9ab23c7ba703ae70ef48a3de55971fc67f27c22","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:18","text":"使用 world space 中的 reference position primitive variable（参考位置 primitive variable）"}
{"id":"487647c574cd75e45f2116f0fb3b40dedfa8993cbb7ed1ebc9f8040f6acd1bee","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:19","text":"只有在"}
{"id":"6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:20","text":"和"}
{"id":"83fc64d737338451fc9aabe94c52d41aa8dd2293fd4e85f86c1e01e0f6eac9b1","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:21","text":"这些 primitive variables 已通过 bridge product 附加到你的几何体时，才可以使用它们。它们通常称为 Reference or Rest pose。请注意，这些只是名称；底层 bridge product 会按这些名称提供数据，而不是由 pattern node 提供。如果使用 Alembic 这类 procedural，请确保导出时已将 Pref 烘焙到对象中。"}
{"id":"c229dc79d74bda0086fc38a46c988d2b857156cd50614ed2f104a97bde056c84","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:22","text":"为什么使用未置换位置？"}
{"id":"33cf779fdb3cd84454dfd45fa3d6caf87973a20c5c41d77d89a30a0f143d5437","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:23","text":"当在 BxDF 和置换中使用相同的 3D 噪声时，应使用 Po，以确保图案对齐。"}
{"id":"6da94174e57953caefa056edbe4464a689cba8828d28db8677be5eeb0fe0fc0e","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:24","text":"Pref"}
{"id":"211bd171002586a7978af58daec5d20c3ee5e8daca872120da1d1d19d327c625","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:25","text":"几何体 Pref 的名称（Maya 使用 __Pref 和 __WPref）。"}
{"id":"e74ea08cfba235dc2ecb51aa5e5432024dbe0efdffe62d857b07abb01eca8884","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:26","text":"仅当"}
{"id":"c36d819e7bc6d2b7da51394411c733db89c395987885ca6770167a3b9bc45c3c","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:27","text":"Use"}
{"id":"a87d7b22807950dcaa04da72ddb56517edecd800ac216270f4dfdb3db3a5e94c","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:28","text":"设置为 \""}
{"id":"59974c3262dbe9bfd4e47201806bc3bb5a630258ddbb078dec8289b21084c3ba","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:29","text":"Deform : __Pref\""}
{"id":"7175517a370b5cd2e664e3fd29c4ea9db5ce17058eb9772fe090a5485e49dad6","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:30","text":"或"}
{"id":"6194be286a138396f1fcba47727280a77a09cbc2d105425681e55b0aeae80283","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:31","text":"\"Deform & transform: __WPref\""}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:32","text":"时，才使用此字段。"}
{"id":"21f08fd2d45b80b119581b5c11d40dfac7d48d0cf3dbecfb43177d13c23729dc","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:33","text":"如果留空，我们会假定使用"}
{"id":"7175517a370b5cd2e664e3fd29c4ea9db5ce17058eb9772fe090a5485e49dad6","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:34","text":"或"}
{"id":"3b606c9b58731adfed73fb84ffd57e47e6e3fdf373022e3fc367a60a842153f8","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:35","text":"，具体取决于当前"}
{"id":"c36d819e7bc6d2b7da51394411c733db89c395987885ca6770167a3b9bc45c3c","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:36","text":"Use"}
{"id":"c6f5b48f4d761c635f40e150a8f9c941288070f606ee9d5d8c35e21986f1e328","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:37","text":"设置。"}
{"id":"b514ebf73921fea11670ca9640e96c27bc4e980867839d368eca5bd872bd174f","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:38","text":"Coordinate System"}
{"id":"b8de9a58642202c40a976d0cf656641568dc5c2f2e4e04ca24f07412ac3c9543","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:39","text":"要应用到 manifold 的坐标系统变换名称。（Maya 称这些为 place3d 节点）。"}
{"id":"be7bebad30a33d81c8545e7ef5230faee4ea1c58bd27e937de7616bc881681fb","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:40","text":"如果留空，我们会使用"}
{"id":"8ba9647d9dc0354acdb1c67c8c0eeb246bd2cb9017659cc24e49755f8bc93014","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:41","text":"object-space"}
{"id":"8870de0df0ccdada725d2dbd90d263477f52acae9d1556a93bf335052256e335","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:42","text":"中的 position，因为这是"}
{"id":"4bc4a7f7d071e8630e9adbe38a1faa7230f9b91367e023014e85669a17037d12","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:43","text":"non-deforming"}
{"id":"9e92fb4d5be54fdeb80c142a6f22b9ed941700b3591452c79a204d6fb2de68ee","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:44","text":"对象所需的。"}
{"id":"3db7c958dfdf5ab8d6e5874200dba26597b825229e0ae2e1ba3fd74632f54aa8","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:45","text":"Warp"}
{"id":"01d69f09d9fc084d389a28ad9937f2d6cedf45a0e3450eb852866c0071b67b0b","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:46","text":"连接噪声或纹理来扭曲定义域"}
{"id":"c8868ef373a3f6688368a7c1564cc04c78f4f1ba69fe99a3acfd61819f0ca3cf","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:47","text":"Warp amount"}
{"id":"4ead2ce6ed752662062f46858ca5957d7d59ddba956246dcafce06d2413bfbba","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:48","text":"用于控制扭曲量的滑块。"}
{"id":"8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:49","text":"Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id":"f6a214f7a5fcda0c2cee9660b7fc29f5649e3c68aad48e20e950137c98913a68","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:50","text":"result"}
{"id":"410cd3cef62b2e902752ea6e43ddf90f78f95a3b5d23bac86ed793bdb2bc8d42","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:51","text":"输出的 3D manifold。"}
{"id":"db7dd1ce0d7ea86988255ca35194b0f1bd3ac901a577cbf001917e21a93cd36c","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:52","text":"resultX"}
{"id":"aa502315570fa2a9c0d9ee32993d204185f0bc160ec0a841105326c24111977e","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:53","text":"manifold 的 X 分量的浮点表示。"}
{"id":"1559ea0c7d8aa4ad51badbe1b30a3a5d7b82932753dbc63044d02897c487480c","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:54","text":"resultY"}
{"id":"e45c354baf56767f0b230b1695bb2654aeed9d96ddbf2d62c4fcb54551ef26a0","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:55","text":"manifold 的 Y 分量的浮点表示。"}
{"id":"153df47561d2ede586a69b0186936cf344555bcbef47ecadd8fbf8b7ce5b2672","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:56","text":"resultZ"}
{"id":"0b2eed571c05fbf7debf7d26e255271429c69719fdbc122e575146357ccf3802","item_id":"0b0b27a43e:57","text":"manifold 的 Z 分量的浮点表示。"}
